# Local development needs NO environment variables.
# Trip state + photos are stored in a local SQLite file at ./data/trip.db.

# On Vercel: add "Blob" storage in your project's Storage tab and Vercel injects
# this token automatically. Its presence switches the app to Vercel Blob storage
# (persistent across serverless requests). You normally never set it by hand.
# BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=vercel_blob_rw_xxxxxxxx
